# ğŸ¥ Medical Management System (Modern)

A complete hospital management desktop application built using Python, Tkinter, SQLite, and ReportLab.  
This system manages doctors, patients, appointments, billing, invoices, and pharmacy inventory â€” all with a clean, modern GUI.

## ğŸš€ Features
- Doctor & Patient Management
- Appointment Scheduling with Conflict Detection
- Medicine & Inventory Management
- Billing and PDF Invoice Generation
- Configurable Clinic Settings
- Dashboard with Stats (Patients, Doctors, Appointments, Inventory)
- Modular Design (Scalable for future features)

## ğŸ› ï¸ Installation
1. Clone the repository
   git clone https://github.com/Parthbhatt11/Medical-Management-System.git

2. Navigate into the folder
   cd Medical-Management-System

3. Install dependencies
   pip install -r requirements.txt

4. Run the application
   python main_modern.py

